  <div class="callout callout-info">
    <strong>Key Finding Summary</strong>
    The project demonstrates exceptional creative architectural thinking. The 7-primitive model, the Hermetic/Yoruba philosophical grounding, the self-modifying graph concept, and the dream-node lateral-reasoning mechanism are all genuinely original contributions to the agent-native computing space. Three blockers prevent production readiness: (1) absent cycle detection creates an infinite-loop DoS vector, (2) hardcoded credentials and SHA-256 password hashing in the live gateway are critical vulnerabilities, and (3) virtually every "advanced" feature (LLM integration, real distributed execution, actual file deployment of rewritten code) is a simulation stub rather than a working implementation.
  </div>

