  <div class="callout callout-high">
    <strong>Finding: Non-standard package.json format</strong>
    The <span class="mono">package.json</span> wraps all metadata under an <span class="mono">_oma_data</span> key with a sibling <span class="mono">_oma_meta</span> key. Standard npm/bun tools will not parse <span class="mono">name</span>, <span class="mono">version</span>, <span class="mono">scripts</span>, or <span class="mono">dependencies</span> from this structure. Running <span class="mono">bun install</span> or <span class="mono">bun run bootstrap</span> will fail. This must be restructured to a standard flat package.json.
